name: THE TICKLE - Issue #35
description:
Art magazine focused on Tezos NFT artists and creative writers.

Issue #35 features artists Tais Koshino (@TaisKoshino), Galo Canizares (@GaloAndStuff) & Ivona Tau (@ivonatau), with a short story by Melanie Golding (@mk_golding).

Created by artists Wily Guys (@guyswily) & Theo Horsmeier (@THorsmeier) and writer Joanne Rush (@JonicolaRush).
